==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: glob
<hw>glob</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>a compact mass, especially
of a semiliquid or viscous substance; <as>as, a <ex>glob</ex> of glue
fell on my shoe</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> ball, clod, lump, clump, chunk.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>global</ent>⟦br⟧
